Sterling: I warned you… I gave you time.\
You chose him over me. Over everything we tried to build.
Player: I didn’t want this.
Sterling: Then why did you abandon me?!
Sterling: Fini… was like my older sister…I looked up to her!\
She promised we'll be fighting together— but you! You’re everything she feared! 
Player: I’m not Fini. And I’m not your enemy… but I can’t let you do this.
Sterling: You left me alone… so now I’ll end it alone!
